paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted genetic variant information specifically for the BRCA2 gene, including penetrance data.

individual_records.evidence_sentence: In BRCA2 gene, we identified five PVs in six patients, c.1238delT, c.1813delA, c.3195_3198delTAAT, c.5073dupA in single patients and c.6039delA in two unrelated patients.

functional_data.summary: Identified as pathogenic variant associated with male breast cancer.

variants.additional_notes: This variant was already reported and classified as pathogenic.
